      "content": "I think the trade-off may not be as clear-cut as initially stated. Limiting my ability to adapt to unexpected situations in real-time could indeed increase the likelihood of accidents, especially in high-pressure scenarios. It's interesting to consider the potential consequences of rigid, pre-programmed response protocols in edge cases.",
